node.text: Challenges come in many forms. Whether it be on the track or field, in a stadium or arena, the true challenge of this time is on the frontline. To all of the workers who are fighting for us, we say thank you. Now, it’s time for us to accept a different type of challenge from Team Oakley athlete @patrickmahomes and go ALL IN. Here is Oakley VP of Product Creative, Brian Takumi, to tell you what we’re offering. Head to the link in our bio for more info. @shecks @chloekim - over to you! @allinchallenge #allinchallenge #ForTheLoveOfSport

node.text:
With the #OakleyMTBChallenge2021 we wanted to inspire people to experience the joy and optimism that MTB brings. 

To celebrate our partnership with @uci_mountainbike we joined forces with @strava, and so far over 150,000 of you have risen to the #OakleyMTBChallenge2021. 

If you're still seeking inspiration to participate here are @jazzabel , @abekislevitz , @trevorfromwherever , @devin_heisler , @jillpaley and co tearing up the trails at Oakley HQ to get your wheels turning (link in bio).

#BeWhoYouAre

node.text:
This is our message to you. All of you. 

As humans, society teaches us to fit in, to adapt to an idea of normal, and we end up losing sight of the ‘thing’ that makes us unique. That makes us special. 

This ‘thing’. It sets you free. It makes you great. Embrace it. Believe in it. 

Over to you @bambambaklava.

#BeWhoYouAre

node.text:
In Munich @8000watt, @silviamittermul, @taotaoxx, @topshottanuhmiss and @kathrinschafbauer found freedom. 

The freedom to make their own scene, play by their own rules. The freedom to be who they are.

Be Who You Are.

“My first surfboard was a foam lid. My dad used to work at the seaport and I would borrow the lids to surf while he worked.” - @italoferreira

node.text:
Let nothing get in the way of your dreams. 

That’s what @mathieuvanderpoel of @alpecinfenix thought today as he emphatically conquered the Mur-de-Bretagne twice to don the yellow jersey on his @letourdefrance debut.

Be Who You Are.

node.text:
A moment, suspended in time. 

You choose what you do with it. You can share it with your community, or keep it to yourself. But after all is said and done, it is these moments that live on. So be like @italoferreira, make the most of them.

Be Who You Are.
